form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: Consulate General of the United States of America Karachi, Pakistan, Form G-146 (c) SPANISH

full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/13/2023 file okg weeps 11/21/7V CONSULATE GENERAL OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA Karachi, Pakistan February 27, 1973 District Director U.S. Department of Justice Immigration and Naturalization Service 300 North Los Angeles St. Los Angeles, California 90012 Dear Sir: Reference: Box A A 19 927 965 Your Form G-146 (c) SPANISH dated February 20, 1973 Mrs. Imtiaz Hussain appeared in the Consular Office of the American Consulate General, Karachi, Pakistan on February 27, 1973 with your Form G-146 (c) SPANISH. She has filled out the form to the best of her knowledge and I am enclosing it for your records. Please be advised that citizens of Pakistan do not speak Spanish. Mrs. Hussain states that she turned in her Form I-94 at Kennedy International Airport New York City upon departure via Pakistan International Airlines on January 20, 1973. Sincerely, Donald R. Woodward Consul 1. 120.93 Enclosure: as stated above. Chre nye
